model

Class Customer

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Customer

  • public class Customer
extends java.lang.Object
    Explanation: This file holds all columns of the CUSTOMER table. It contains private variables for each column, a constructor to initialize them, and getters and setters for each. The variables are created as properties. References: http://www.swtestacademy.com/database-operations-javafx/ https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=H1mePFyqqiE&t=18s
    Version:
    24/11/2017
    Author:
    Michael Aring
